22:03.040 --> 22:09.960
So in the late 70s and through the 80s, early 80s, UFO researchers could petition the government for documents.

22:10.100 --> 22:14.720
And they were getting thousands of pages of documents related to UFOs.

22:14.820 --> 22:16.060
This was a shocking thing.

22:16.440 --> 22:23.920
You know, all through the 50s and 60s and most of the 70s, the government agencies, CIA, FBI, military agencies,

22:23.920 --> 22:25.740
said, look, we don't really do this.

22:26.120 --> 22:27.100
